review.reviewBody:
We ordered 1.Egg Tofu w/ shrimp paste, 3.ShiuMai, Bean Curd with Enoki,Radish cake in XO and Sticky rice w/sausage. Everything was excellent except the egg tofu was bland, no flavour. ShiuMai are enormous!
will definitely order again!
First time eating here. It was amazing I taste and size and packing as we had delivery! Will go back   The menu looks great.

One of the best Curry Beefs I've had, lots of veggies, amazing potatoes, and tender slices of beef. the S&S Pork was also great, not overly saucy either. Egg tarts were the flaky kind and well above expectation. Everything wasn't overly salty, unlike most takeout places. A new favorite of ours.
The Braised Cod with Tofu Hot Pot is awesome.  I love the cod and and the taste is amazing.  Not too and salty and a big portion  This  is going in  my rotation.
So yummy! Love the pan 32. Pan Fried Chive Dumplings 32. 香煎韮菜棵, 3. Steamed Shiu-Mai Dumplings 3. 魚子北菇燒賣, 2. Steamed Prawn Dumplings 2. 西湖蝦餃皇   the size of the dumpling are huge! Highly recommend.
